stars

  • Classes in stars used by stars
    Class Description
    Admin
    Represents an Admin in the system.
    Course
    Represents a course in the system A course belongs to one School, can have multiple indexes, and is of one of the course types specified in the num CourseType
    CourseType
    Enum of the course type of all courses
    DisplayErrorMsgUI
    Abstract method to display error message in the UI
    FileController
    Controller class to handle the logic for retrieving data from files in required format and saving data to binary files
    Index
    represents the Index of a course belongs to a single Course
    LessonType
    Enum of the lesson type of all study groups
    Notifications
    interface for defining a function to send notification
    PrintMenuUI
    interface to print menu for UI
    RegisteredCourse
    represents a course registration by a student to a particular index can have RegisteredCourse.regStatus of Waitlist or Registered
    Review
    Association class to store a review written by Student for a particular Course
    School
    Represents a School in the system contains myltiple Students and Courses
    Student
    Represents a Student in the system
    StudyGroup
    Contains the lesson information of a particular lesson belonging to an index can be of the types specified in enum LessonType
    User
    Represents users in the system Users can be students or Admin
    ValidateIntController
    Controller class to ensure input by a user is as required
    WeekType
    Enum of the week types
